---
import Main from '../layouts/Main.astro';
---
<Main title="Mathematics" description="Free mathematics education from Class 9 to 12 with step-by-step solutions." activeNav="math">

<style>
  .math-hero {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 60px 24px 40px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .math-hero h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .math-hero h1 span {
    color: var(--teal);
  }

  .math-hero p {
    color: var(--txt2);
    font-size: 1rem;
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  .chapters-grid {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px 60px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .chapter-card {
    background: var(--surf);
    border: 1px solid var(--bdr);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .chapter-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--teal);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(78, 201, 176, 0.1);
  }

  .chapter-num {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--teal);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .chapter-card h3 {
    font-size: 18px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: var(--txt);
  }

  .chapter-card p {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--txt2);
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .chapter-link {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: gap 0.2s;
  }

  .chapter-card:hover .chapter-link {
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .section-label {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 40px auto 20px;
    padding: 0 24px;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--mut);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
  }

  .section-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--bdr);
  }

  .legacy-link {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 24px 60px;
  }

  .legacy-link a {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 12px 20px;
    background: var(--surf);
    border: 1px solid var(--bdr);
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: var(--txt2);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 14px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
  }

  .legacy-link a:hover {
    border-color: var(--amb);
    color: var(--amb);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .math-hero {
      padding: 40px 16px 32px;
    }

    .chapters-grid {
      padding: 0 16px 40px;
    }

    .section-label {
      padding: 0 16px;
    }

    .legacy-link {
      padding: 0 16px 40px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="math-hero">
  <h1><span>Mathematics</span></h1>
  <p>Free, step-by-step education from Class 9 to 12. Master fundamentals through interactive lessons and solved examples.</p>
</div>

<div class="section-label">
  📖 Class 9 Chapters
</div>

<div class="chapters-grid">
  <a href="/math/chapter-1-number-systems" class="chapter-card">
    <div class="chapter-num">Chapter 1</div>
    <h3>Number Systems</h3>
    <p>Master natural, whole, integer, rational, irrational, and real numbers. Understand the hierarchy and operations.</p>
    <span class="chapter-link">Read Chapter →</span>
  </a>

  <div class="chapter-card" style="opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed;">
    <div class="chapter-num">Chapter 2</div>
    <h3>Polynomials</h3>
    <p>Coming soon — factors, zeros, and polynomial division.</p>
    <span class="chapter-link" style="color: var(--mut);">Coming Soon</span>
  </div>

  <div class="chapter-card" style="opacity: 0.6; cursor: not-allowed;">
    <div class="chapter-num">Chapter 3</div>
    <h3>Coordinate Geometry</h3>
    <p>Coming soon — distance, section formula, and lines.</p>
    <span class="chapter-link" style="color: var(--mut);">Coming Soon</span>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="section-label">
  📚 Full Mathematics Guide
</div>

<div class="legacy-link">
  <a href="/math.html">
    ← View Complete Mathematics Guide (Class 9–12)
  </a>
</div>

</Main>
